{"tid":1525120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全面開啟升級抗爭!!罷工頻率提升至每周一罷!!!","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:17:50.000Z","uid":47659,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a391b06d2415bb94de8990c0e6971d1073e4afbf","tid":1525120,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:40.000Z","msg":"幫手開post, 樓主推極都無人理<br />\n原post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1525035/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1525035/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網民問卷調查報告</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我們在這<strong>沉痛</strong>的晚上公佈 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">感謝各位支持</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">三九六四</span></ins></strong>位網民參與</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k45jMPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk45jMPC.jpg&h=d16e0065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>數據反映</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>打工仔老闆們</strong>堅定的<strong>抗爭意志</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yw7RCWv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyw7RCWv.jpg&h=9fe23164&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/doE8E9R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdoE8E9R.jpg&h=3e279fee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZBh983b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBh983b.jpg&h=fe7c774c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2KgO3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2KgO3d.jpg&h=62103e87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYavTuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYavTuT.jpg&h=4c7649eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＊參與界別逾40個行業<br />\n＊若九月首輛罷工(9/2 - 9/3)被政府無視，65.9%投選九月第二星期(9/9)開展下回罷工<br />\n＊最多人選擇「持續每週罷一兩天」，亦多人願意「升級持續三天」，甚至「無限期」罷至政府答應訴求<br />\n＊50.5%投選「以病假或事假形式罷工」，25%即「不請假直接以罷工明志」<br />\n＊考慮升級罷工的主要因素為：23.2%「收入減少至直接影響生計」，22.2％「公司政見不同或備受打壓，擔心自己會被清算」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>我們呼籲</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>社會各界</strong>請為升級罷工<strong>作好準備</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sjbi2r7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjbi2r7.jpg&h=e8d35ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求大家，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工止暴</span></strong><br />\n唔好再俾喱幾個數字上升：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6人死，3隻眼，900人被捕，無數骨折受傷...<br />\n</span><br />\nSummer on fire. If we burn, you burn with us. <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">八三一</span></strong>只是開始，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九一</span></strong>機場和你塞，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九二九三</span></strong>大三罷，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>下一步</strong></span>係？<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">香港打工仔老闆們要連成一線</span>，罷工罷市，先破後立，光復香港。<br />\n我們將重建一個打工打到變皇帝，人人安居樂業，有尊嚴的香港。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>齊心就事成</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>請一起堅持到勝利一天 <br />\n約定於煲底除口罩相見</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n前文提要：<br />\n【升級罷工全民自決】網民發起問卷調查！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508197</a><br />\n<br />\n上回講到：<br />\n【升級罷工全民自決】一名打工仔升級罷工決策考慮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511688</a><br />\n<br />\n最終回：<br />\n【升級罷工全民自決】Final call!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516317</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnQ4dwB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnQ4dwB.jpg&h=b7314f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#數據抗議 #統計救國"},{"pid":"74f86e7f0ebdb9e187627e36d55904a97b4b0fdc","tid":1525120,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b38b2a8ff610cc71512522eb642fb8111be61f4","tid":1525120,"uid":261971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zthyLN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zthyLN.png&h=bc898463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb2da9111acb24f59ec8e2c03b5b274e3dc2e15","tid":1525120,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:48:51.000Z","msg":"可能佢p牌推唔起"},{"pid":"131c6ecfc5c33692e26d15abeb70d94341f5843a","tid":1525120,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9aafb03ba9b13159bfb8f652ef8b1c4476e7d6c","tid":1525120,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:30.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"a6c1b7e8d7ef4796827920cd25bc34a3bbbb24b1","tid":1525120,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:51:54.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"3bc9063cd82171d172044ad3e21575b53d5fa830","tid":1525120,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:53:12.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"43085549c7541b5bfed1f71f9d072f2aa479063f","tid":1525120,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:56:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9601e1228b45c42e6be454eb121e905fa079ef6","tid":1525120,"uid":157103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:12:53.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好入晒機場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58f35e8e9e75deaeaef0de0dc8f949d29dc7147","